Pustite me.


1162
01:17:17.570 --> 01:17:19.766
Pomakni, pomaknite se, pomaknite,
pomaknite, pomaknite, pomaknite!


1163
01:17:19.770 --> 01:17:21.841
- Zaustavi!
- Uđite u sastav, svi vi!


1164
01:17:21.850 --> 01:17:23.079
STOP!

1165
01:17:23.730 --> 01:17:25.289
Rekao sam, prestani!

1166
01:17:25.570 --> 01:17:27.163
Uskoro će biti mrak.

1167
01:17:27.850 --> 01:17:29.443
Razaq!

1168
01:17:29.930 --> 01:17:32.047
Razaq! Razaq!

1169
01:17:43.770 --> 01:17:46.922
Sulayman... Sulayman!

1170
01:17:48.370 --> 01:17:49.645
<i>Ogledalo sjaji!</i>

1171
01:17:50.490 --> 01:17:52.243
<i>Koristite ga za slijepe jaguarima!</i>

1172
01:18:04.490 --> 01:18:06.225
<i>A onda zamke!</i>

1173
01:18:06.260 --> 01:18:07.961
<i>Bacite je preko njih!</i>

1174
01:18:45.090 --> 01:18:48.083
Razaq! Razaq! Razaq!

1175
01:18:48.650 --> 01:18:49.845
Došao sam za svog oca!

1176
01:18:50.250 --> 01:18:51.650
Došao sam za moju bebu!

1177
01:18:52.730 --> 01:18:54.084
Spusti ga!

1178
01:18:55.090 --> 01:18:57.082
Rekao sam ga, spusti ga!

1179
01:19:03.090 --> 01:19:05.002
Vidite li što se događa?

1180
01:19:05.690 --> 01:19:08.285
Gdje ga vodiš?
Tko je vani?


1181
01:19:09.090 --> 01:19:10.570
Gledaj dalje, zar ne?

1182
01:19:11.330 --> 01:19:13.128
To je samo jedan čovjek.
Kakve to ima veze?


1183
01:19:15.050 --> 01:19:17.565
IĆI!

1184
01:19:20.290 --> 01:19:21.406
IĆI!

1185
01:19:21.410 --> 01:19:23.163
Idite, osim ako me ne ubijete!

1186
01:19:27.090 --> 01:19:29.605
Vrištat ću i proklinjati te

1187
01:19:29.610 --> 01:19:33.286
sve dok posljednji dah
ne napusti moje tijelo.


1188
01:19:33.930 --> 01:19:34.602
Ići!

1189
01:19:38.890 --> 01:19:39.767
Ti si lud.

1190
01:19:40.850 --> 01:19:41.647
Lud!

1191
01:19:43.410 --> 01:19:45.288
Ovdje možete umrijeti
zbog svega što me briga!


1192
