1227
01:22:03.530 --> 01:22:05.010
<i>Zato što je to bio kraj.</i>

1228
01:22:08.650 --> 01:22:10.209
<i>Slon je preobrazen!</i>

1229
01:22:10.650 --> 01:22:12.881
<i>Uzeo je vreću sjemena
iz središta planine</i>


1230
01:22:12.890 --> 01:22:14.802
<i>i vratio ga Sulaymanu!</i>

1231
01:22:15.650 --> 01:22:17.801
<i>Sulayman se vratio u svoje selo.</i>

1232
01:22:18.690 --> 01:22:19.975
<i>Bilo je puno plesa.</i>

1233
01:22:20.010 --> 01:22:22.730
<i>I pjevanje. 
I smijali se.</i>

1234
01:22:22.765 --> 01:22:24.847
<i>I jesti.</i>

1235
01:22:32.090 --> 01:22:33.490
Razaq!

1236
01:22:39.530 --> 01:22:41.840
Baba! Baba!

1237
01:22:42.650 --> 01:22:44.084
Je li živ?

1238
01:22:45.090 --> 01:22:46.240
Nije njegova krv.

1239
01:22:47.010 --> 01:22:48.239
On živi.

1240
01:23:09.130 --> 01:23:10.769
Izlazi odavde, dijete.
Idite dalje!


1241
01:23:11.730 --> 01:23:13.403
Što je brže moguće.

1242
01:24:16.210 --> 01:24:19.681
To je mjesec.

1243
01:24:27.530 --> 01:24:28.850
Soraya...

1244
01:24:29.810 --> 01:24:31.961
S... Sora... SORAYA!

1245
01:24:31.970 --> 01:24:35.646
- Mama?
- Soraya!


1246
01:24:35.650 --> 01:24:38.245
Soraya... Zaki...

1247
01:24:41.250 --> 01:24:43.367
<i>Mi smo zemlja</i>

1248
01:24:43.370 --> 01:24:44.201
<i>čiji su ljudi</i>

1249
01:24:44.210 --> 01:24:46.486
<i>su njeno najveće blago.</i>

1250
01:24:50.650 --> 01:24:52.687
<i>Mi smo na rubovima carstva</i>

1251
01:24:52.690 --> 01:24:54.647
<i>u ratu jedni s drugima.</i>

1252
01:25:00.610 --> 01:25:02.522
Parvana...

1253
01:25:04.570 --> 01:25:06.323
Mi smo lomljena
zemlja u kandžama


1254
01:25:06.330 --> 01:25:08.526
od planina Hindu Kush,

1255
01:25:08.530 --> 01:25:11.887
opaljen vatrenim očima
sjevernih pustinja.


1256
01:25:13.810 --> 01:25:15.164
Crna ruševna zemlja

1257
01:25:15.170 --> 01:25:17.526
protiv vrhova leda.

1258
01:25:19.890 --> 01:25:21.768
<i>Mi smo... Auriana,</i>

1259
01:25:23.010 --> 01:25:24.763
<i>zemlja plemića.</i>

1260
01:25:27.130 --> 01:25:29.725
<i>Podignite svoja srca,
a ne svoj glas.</i>


1261
01:25:30.890 --> 01:25:32.802
<i>To je kiša koja cvjetovi rastu.</i>

